query:
SELECT 
  nome,
  dum,
  dataUltrassom,
  igUltrassomSemanas,
  igUltrassomDias,
  DATEDIFF('2024-12-30', dum) as dias_desde_dum,
  FLOOR(DATEDIFF('2024-12-30', dum) / 7) as semanas_calculadas,
  MOD(DATEDIFF('2024-12-30', dum), 7) as dias_calculados
FROM gestantes 
WHERE nome = 'TESTE - Gestante Exemplo';
